dcterms:description: WebQSP is a relatively small dataset consisting of 3098 train and 1639 test questions which cover 3794 and 2002 entities respectively. It contains a mixture of simple and complex questions.
dcterms:title: WebQSP

dcterms:description: SimpleQuestions consists only of simple questions, with a training set of more than 30,000 questions and a test set of close to 10,000 questions. It was originally based on Freebase and later converted to Wikidata IDs.
dcterms:title: SimpleQuestions

dcterms:creator: M. Dubey

dcterms:description: LC-QuAD 2.0 is a large and varied dataset comprising of 24180 train questions and 6046 test questions, covering 33609 and 8417 entities respectively. It includes a mixture of simple and complex questions verbalised by human workers.
dcterms:title: LC-QuAD 2.0
